reviewText: Hubby & I thought we would watch something that seemed sexual yet comical...absolutely can not believe we wasted our money!  However we did not waste any time throwing this in the trash!  Didn't even watch it for 10 minutes, fast forwarded through much of it to see if it would get any better but to no avail.  I don't even think 20-somethings would find this entertaining.
This DVD sucks boring as he'll it's like the dr. Seuss of spanking not hot
Very funny I sent as a gag gift and they loved it.
I bought this thing expecting turgid prose in favor of sexual corporal punishment.  I never knew spanking could be so funny as it is presented here.
